snippet.title: Armored Warfare - Xbox Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more: https:/aw-xbox.my.com/

Armored Warfare will be released to the Microsoft Xbox® One console on August 2, 2018!

Become a modern tank mercenary commander, take control of cutting-edge tanks and join your friends in completing co-op missions, compete with rival teams in PvP mode, or experience the real tank action in the Global Operations – an explosive mix of competitive and cooperative play empowered by large maps with respawn zones, surveillance drones, AI support, airstrikes, and much more.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ArmoredWarfareXbox/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ArmoredWarXBOX
Discord: https://discord.gg/UYp2Szr

What is Armored Warfare?

We are proud to present Armored Warfare. Armored Warfare is a free-to-play massively multiplayer online tactical military video game that puts you in control of modern tanks, armored vehicles and more! Armored Warfare features stunning next-gen visuals, dynamic destructible environments, customizable vehicles and intense team-based gameplay where players work to crush each other with the power of modern combat vehicles in a free-to-compete experience!

#ArmoredWarfare #XBOX
